divs: Sighting DetailsI traveled to the Grand Canyon with my family and while taking a burst of photographs of a Condor flying in the air I caught what appears to be a reflective round circle in the distance. I did not notice the object in the air while I was taking the images. It was only after I had returned to my home and was reviewing my photographs that I was puzzled at what I had captured. It could be nothing as the object appears very far, however I will include the original unedited images so it can be analyzed properly.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Grand Canyon Natl. Park
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: Object appear on photographs during trip to the Grand Canyon
